                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18430508-name-1099" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18430508-name-1099" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18430508-name-1099" type="surname" value="CLARKE"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18430508-name-1099" type="given" value="THOMAS"></interp>THOMAS CLARKE</persName>
                  </hi>. I am shopman to Thomas Vesper, a pawnbroker, in Grenada-terrace, Commercial-road. On the 28th of April, I had a pistol—I saw it safe a week before—this is it—it is my master's—I know it by the fellow one—I will swear to it—I have seen the prisoner about the door.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
